                                    <p class="card-text">Learn the simplest way to select the object and change
                                        dimensions.
                                    </p>
                                </div>

                                <div class="card-footer pt-0">
                                    <a t-att-title="post.name" class="card-link" t-att-href="post.website_url">Learn more
